Program of Support Services to Rural Markets
Programa de Servicios de Apoyo a los Mercados Rurales

description.narrative: The objective of the proposed program is to improve rural producers' access to dynamic markets for goods and services, both within and outside Peru, by providing services such as business information and training and, in so doing, boost their income. The technical-assistance and lending services will be an outgrowth of the relationships the producers establish with business advisory service providers and the buyers of their products.
